Module com.electra.canbusdemo
Package com.electra.canbusdemo

Class MainViewStaticVariables

java.lang.Object
com.electra.canbusdemo.MainViewStaticVariables
public class MainViewStaticVariables extends Object
This class contains static variables representing various constants used in the application. These constants include mode names, message IDs, offsets, and other values that are utilized throughout the application for maintaining consistency and ease of reference.

The class provides getter methods for accessing these constants.

Note: The values stored in this class are considered constants and should not be modified during runtime.
